    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-technology\">significant</span> upgrade for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Exosuit Aeration Membrane</span>. Use <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> to begin upgrade <VAL_ON>installation process<>.<br><br>The module is flexible, and exact upgrade statistics are <span class=\"name name-special\">unknown</span> until installation is complete.<br><br>Significantly improves survival times <span class=\"name name-technology\">underwater</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "对<span class=\"name name-technology\">套装曝气膜</span>的<span class=\"name name-technology\">显著</span>提升。使用<VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><>开始<VAL_ON>安装升级<>。<br><br>该模块很灵活，具体升级信息在安装结束前<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>显著提升<span class=\"name name-technology\">水下</span>生存时间。",
